data.description: Courtyard Manor's newest listing offers 5BR/4.5BA all brick home w/timeless architecture & comfortable elegance. Spacious 2-story foyer welcomes into an   open floor plan & freshly painted main level living: Grt rm w/builtin shelving, formal dining, beautiful kitchen w/pantry, casual dining w/bar seating, stainless applcs; master suite feat. HUGE walk-in closet that connects to laundry!!, sep vanities/sep tub & shower; 2 additional Bedrooms w/hardwoods Jack-n-Jill Bathroom w/sep vanities. Outdoor living & entertaining is seamless w/screened & grilling deck leads to fire pit & BIG FENCED backyard. Upper level loft bonus rm w/Bedroom & ensuite bath. Thoughtful design & craftsmanship is evident w/built ins, generous storage, arched cased openings, central vacuum, timeless finishes, sprinkler system & NEW ROOF 2021! The full 3000+ sq.ft. in basement is heated & cooled w/new BR & full bath. Large Lot & 2 Car Main Level Garage +1 more bsmt garage space to pull in equipment, car, boat, etc.
